      .main-introduction__title
        %h2
          FURIMAが選ばれる3つの理由
        .main-introduction__title-after
      %ul.main-introduction__list
        %li.main-introduction__left-list
          .main-introduction__left-img
            %span.number 1
            =image_tag 'pict/pict-reason-01.jpg' , size:261
          .main-introduction__left-text
            %h3
              %span 3分
              ですぐに出品
          .main-introduction__left-sub-text
            %p
              スマホで入力するだけで簡単に出品できる！
        %li.main-introduction__center-list
          .main-introduction__center-img
            %span.number 2
            =image_tag 'pict/pict-reason-02.jpg', size:261
          .main-introduction__center-text
            %h3
              %span シンプル
              で使いやすい
          .main-introduction__center-sub-text
            %p
              めんどくさい入力は必要なく、検索も購入もスムーズ！
        %li.main-introduction__right-list
          .main-introduction__right-img
            %span.number 3
            =image_tag 'pict/pict-reason-03.jpg' , size:261
          .main-introduction__right-text
            %h3
              手数料
              %span 業界最安
          .main-introduction__right-sub-text
            %p
              最大3%でお得に出品&購入！
    .middle-visual
      .middle-visual__inner
        %h2.middle-visual__title 会員数日本一位
